-- Sistema to Buy $62 Million Treasury Stock of Bashneft Refineries
-- B y   A n n a   S h i r y a e v s k a y a
-- 2012-09-28T17:13:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-28/sistema-to-buy-62-million-treasury-stock-of-bashneft-refineries.html
Billionaire Vladimir Evtushenkov’s
AFK Sistema, a controlling shareholder of OAO Bashneft, will buy
treasury shares in the oil producer’s refining and marketing
units for 1.92 billion rubles ($62 million).  The shares of OAO  Ufa Oil Refinery (UNPZ) , OAO Novoil and OAO
Ufaneftekhim will be exchanged for Bashneft stock next month, as
the company consolidates its refining and marketing units,
Bashneft said today in an e-mailed statement. Sistema will gain
an additional stake of 0.6 percent in the oil producer,
according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
